#                                                                                                  #
#  Sets up Catch using ExternalProject_Add.                                                        #
#                                                                                                  #
#  Variables set and cached by this module are:                                                    #
#    CatchSourceDir (required for subsequent include_directories calls)                            #
#                                                                                                  #
